This is the README file for WWW::REST, base class for REST resources.

Please type "perldoc WWW::REST" after installation to see the module
usage information.

* Installation

WWW::REST uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

